\@writefile{lot}{\contentsline {table}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Cumulative mode-switching statistics across phases. H3: global anchored fraction (both modes ``substantially present''). Variance test: chi-square test of between-conversation variance vs.\ Bernoulli null (Section~\ref {sec:method}). $\text  {$\mathsurround \z@ \mathchar "458$}$~H3 confirmed at all scales. H1 (run-length persistence) was tested with a corrected parametric bootstrap on all $N=24$ conversations (27~anchored runs): bootstrap $p=0.557$, $\chi ^2$ $p=0.218$, both non-significant; see Section~\ref {subsec:h1}. All intermediate H1 p-values computed with scipy's \texttt  {kstest} are invalid on discrete data and are omitted here.}}{5}{table.1}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{tab:cascade}{{1}{5}{Cumulative mode-switching statistics across phases. H3: global anchored fraction (both modes ``substantially present''). Variance test: chi-square test of between-conversation variance vs.\ Bernoulli null (Section~\ref {sec:method}). $\checkmark $~H3 confirmed at all scales. H1 (run-length persistence) was tested with a corrected parametric bootstrap on all $N=24$ conversations (27~anchored runs): bootstrap $p=0.557$, $\chi ^2$ $p=0.218$, both non-significant; see Section~\ref {subsec:h1}. All intermediate H1 p-values computed with scipy's \texttt {kstest} are invalid on discrete data and are omitted here}{table.1}{}}
